唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyloc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=f117d59b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ade0e80e49a43c850085192b9557b9fe2f4f71","tid":1745283,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"你究竟講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0e447b6a099e08ac1fc45454a9645ea38e772f","tid":1745283,"uid":9398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"即是魏晉，總之停左辦魏晉科舉學校，<br />\n咁是咪唔會有魏晉的學士的資格=冇魏晉學士<br />\n提供比當時朝廷=冇官用？"}]}